---
---

<!-- About Section -->
<section id="about" class="py-24 px-6 relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-6xl">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
            <div class="relative reveal">
                <div class="aspect-square glass-card rounded-[4rem] p-4 border border-white/10 overflow-hidden relative">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1522071820081-009f0129c71c?q=80&w=1000&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Team" class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-[3.5rem]">
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-dark/60 to-transparent rounded-[3.5rem]"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="absolute -bottom-10 -right-6 glass-card p-10 rounded-[3rem] border border-white/10 shadow-2xl backdrop-blur-xl">
                    <div class="text-5xl font-black text-[#6366f1] mb-2">50+</div>
                    <div class="text-sm font-bold text-white/60 tracking-widest uppercase">Klien Puas</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="reveal">
                <div class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 mb-6 rounded-full border border-[#6366f1]/30 bg-[#6366f1]/10 text-[#6366f1] text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">
                    Digitalisasi Tanpa Ribet
                </div>
                <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-8 leading-tight tracking-tight">Gowkan adalah Solusi <span class="text-[#6366f1]">Naik Kelas</span> Dunia Digital.</h2>
                <p class="text-white/60 text-lg mb-8 leading-relaxed font-medium">
                    Gowkan hadir sebagai mitra strategis bagi para pengusaha yang ingin naik kelas ke dunia digital tanpa harus pusing dengan urusan teknis yang rumit. Kami percaya bahwa teknologi tinggi tidak harus mahal dan membingungkan.
                </p>
                <p class="text-white/60 text-lg mb-8 leading-relaxed font-medium italic">
                    Kami fokus pada tiga pilar utama: Kecepatan Akses, Desain Minimalis yang Menjual, dan Efisiensi Biaya. Bersama Gowkan, aset digital Anda akan bekerja 24 jam untuk mendatangkan pelanggan.
                </p>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-10">
                    <div class="glass-card p-6 rounded-3xl border border-white/10">
                        <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-[#6366f1]/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-[#6366f1] mb-4">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="font-bold mb-2">Kecepatan</h4>
                        <p class="text-xs text-white/40 leading-relaxed font-medium">Website super cepat tanpa loading lama.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="glass-card p-6 rounded-3xl border border-white/10">
                        <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-[#a855f7]/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-[#a855f7] mb-4">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 21a4 4 0 01-4-4V5a2 2 0 012-2h4a2 2 0 012 2v12a4 4 0 01-4 4zm0 0h12a2 2 0 002-2v-4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2.343M11 7.343l1.657-1.657a2 2 0 012.828 0l2.829 2.829a2 2 0 010 2.828l-8.486 8.485M7 17h.01" />
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="font-bold mb-2">Desain</h4>
                        <p class="text-xs text-white/40 leading-relaxed font-medium">Visual modern dan UI/UX yang disesuaikan dengan karakter perusahan.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
